definitely don't use the recommended concentration if I'm soaking for
days.  I'd say that if I fill the carboy all the way up and I'm aiming
for at least a couple days soak (I often end up letting them sit in the
stuff all week) then I'll toss in a few tablespoons.  Of course, if you
